528
00:40:48,200 --> 00:40:49,700
Kerstman?

529
00:40:55,100 --> 00:40:56,200
Wat?

530
00:40:56,400 --> 00:40:59,000
Ik heb wat jus d'orange voor u.

531
00:41:02,300 --> 00:41:04,800
Wat zit erin?
